label.value: VLMC L1-5 PDGFRA COLEC12 primary motor cortex vascular leptomeningeal cell (Hsap)

value.value: A vascular leptomeningeal cell of the Homo sapiens primary motor cortex. These cells can be distinguished from other cells in the primary motor cortex by their selective expression of COL1A2 (Hsap), COLEC12 (Hsap). These cells also express PDGFRA (Hsap), COLEC12 (Hsap). The reference data for this cell type is CS201912131_126.
